 Hi, 
 What I expected from the code editor is, that it should behave like any other text editor - notepad, ultraEdit and so on. For example if you select one row, you can deselect it by holding down shift and pressing home, and again select the whole row by holding down shift and pressing end button. 
 Of course the selection performed at step 3 could be changed to something more "racket" specific - for example holding down shift and pressing end will trigger a selection of the code between the corresponding brackets (for ex. 4th opening and 4th closing bracket); or holding down shift and pressing end will deselect the code between corresponding brackets. I'll leave the implementation to you, as I'm sure you'll come with a good idea. 
 Regards, 
